HEADWORD: Brobdingnagian
<hw>Brob`ding*nag"i*an</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<ets>Brobdingnag</ets>, a country of giants in ⟦ldquo⟧Gulliver's
Travels.⟦rdquo⟧]</ety> <def>Colossal; of extraordinary height;
gigantic.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A giant.</def></def2>
<altsp>[Spelt often <asp>Brobdignagian</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

